Assignment 2.00/1.10 for Coms 327
Made by Trevor Luster with solution code from Jeremy Shaeffer
[2017-04-15]

Added ranged combat.

Added 3 bars of meter for the PC to powerful special ranged moves.

Implemented PC equipment defence. Armor damage scaling uses the
knockback calculation algorithm from Super Smash Bros. Melee. It
has been modified heavily to work with this game's variables and
scale properly. The algorithm used can be found here:
https://www.ssbwiki.com/Knockback#Melee_onward
